    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone seeking reliable daily transportation. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are solid, and it starts reliably every morning. However, please note that the exterior shows its age with some visible paint fading on the roof and minor dings on the passenger side door. The interior is clean but has some wear on the driver's seat upholstery. It is a great, honest car for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics.",
